text: Im Gyeong-seok (born 19 September 1968) is a South Korean rower. He competed in the men's single sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in rowing Category:Rowers at the 1990 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 1990 Asian Games
